===============================  CFJ 3690  ===============================

      G. possesses at least one blot.

==========================================================================

Caller:                        twg

Judge:                         D. Margaux
Judgement:                     FALSE

==========================================================================

History:

Called by twg:                                    01 Dec 2018 00:19:00
Assigned to ATMunn:                               03 Dec 2018 01:02:00
ATMunn recused:                                   25 Dec 2018 21:56:00
